		<title>狗狗失蹤多半就在附近！第一時間要找的「藏匿點」曝光</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/14/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e5%a4%b1%e8%b9%a4%e5%a4%9a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b0%b1%e5%9c%a8%e9%99%84%e8%bf%91%ef%bc%81%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e6%99%82%e9%96%93%e8%a6%81%e6%89%be%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e8%97%8f%e5%8c%bf%e9%bb%9e/</link>
		
